<div class="slide"><h4 class="new">Page counters</h4>
  <div class="slidecontent">
  <ul>
      <li>insert whereever you want an empty element of class __FScounter that will contain the current slide's index</li>
      <li>insert whereever you want an empty element of class __FStotal that will contain the total number of slides in the show</li>
    </ul>
   <p>For instance:</p>
   <pre>&lt;div class="footer"&gt;
  &lt;span class="__FScounter" /&gt; / &lt;span class="__FStotal" /&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</pre>
  </div>
</div>

